      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Example Payload\n\n```json\n{\n  \"errorCode\": \"MISSING_TARGET\",\n  \"title\": \"Missing target\",\n  \"message\": \"The consumed surface could not resolve its source node.\",\n  \"severity\": \"error\",\n  \"targetRef\": \"/tasks/interaction-policy/root.node\",\n  \"expected\": \"interaction-policy-task-summary\",\n  \"repairHint\": \"Point sourceNodeId at an exposed summary node.\"\n}\n```",
