      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Adoption Notes\n\nRoute existing blank-shell failures through this message shape first, then hand the normalized payload to a shared `error-card` node class. That lets multiple renderers reuse the same fallback surface without inventing one-off schemas.",
