      "width": 560,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Canonical Fields\n\nThe first shared error message shape is:\n\n- `errorCode`\n- `title`\n- `message`\n- `severity`\n- `targetRef`\n- `expected`\n- `repairHint`\n\nOnly the first four are required in every case. The last three are optional but should be included whenever the renderer has them.",
